Welcome to Spurs! I'm 100% behind this signing...

Quick, strong, direct, versatile, technically gifted with goals and assists to boot 👌👍

Just remember bro, not even Messi or Ronaldo can be at their best with the ball every game, but every player has the power to give 100% without the ball - being brave, willing to tackle, closing down and fighting for the shirt...And 100% in gratitude and attitude... If you always do this, we will always be behind you...this is precisely why Son, Moura and Lamela have always had the support. They've all had ups and downs but never complained, always played with a smile, passion and give 100% for the shirt in whatever minutes they've been given on the pitch!

Best of luck for the years to come! COYS! 😊👏
